@NODE   readme
@TITLE  "Cookie / Read me"

    WHAT IS COOKIE ?

Cookie is a full system conform written database for "cookies"
how need in mailprograms. This is often much easier than write
long lists of cookies.

Everybody who works and handles with cookies needs Cookie !


    CARDWARE

Please note that Cookie is cardware. This means that everybody, who
uses Cookie, has to send a postcard or an email to the @{"author" LINK contact}.


    CREDITS

I have to thank Reinold Sadlo for his good betatesting!


    Have fun with Cookie !!
@ENDNODE

@NODE   using
@TITLE  "Cookie / Using"

The using of Cookie is very simple, because it is an easy database
and so only the button gadgets are described in this guide:

    @{" First " LINK firstlast} @{" Prev " LINK prevnext} @{" Add  " LINK add} @{" Del   " LINK del} @{" Next  " LINK prevnext} @{" Last " LINK firstlast}

    @{" Flush " LINK flush} @{" Load " LINK load} @{" Save " LINK save} @{" Print " LINK print} @{" About " LINK about} @{" Quit " LINK quit}
@ENDNODE

